#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn12.59"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn12.59:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.59:0.2"
msgid "6. Dukkhavagga "
msgstr "6. Suffering "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn12.59:0.3"
msgid "59. Viññāṇasutta "
msgstr "59. Consciousness "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn12.59:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.59:1.2"
msgid "“Saṃyojaniyesu, bhikkhave, dhammesu assādānupassino viharato viññāṇassa avakkanti hoti. "
msgstr "“There are things that are prone to being fettered. When you concentrate on the gratification provided by these things, consciousness is conceived. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.59:1.3"
msgid "Viññāṇapaccayā nāmarūpaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "Consciousness is a condition for name and form. … "

msgctxt "sn12.59:1.4"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. "
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering originates. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn12.59:2.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, mahārukkho. "
msgstr "Suppose there was a great tree. "

msgctxt "sn12.59:2.2"
msgid "Tassa yāni ceva mūlāni … pe … "
msgstr "And its roots going downwards and across all draw the sap upwards. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.59:2.3"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, saṃyojaniyesu dhammesu assādānupassino viharato viññāṇassa avakkanti hoti … pe …. "
msgstr "In the same way, there are things that are prone to being fettered. When you concentrate on the gratification provided by these things, consciousness is conceived. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn12.59:3.1"
msgid "Saṃyojaniyesu, bhikkhave, dhammesu ādīnavānupassino viharato viññāṇassa avakkanti na hoti. "
msgstr "There are things that are prone to being fettered. When you concentrate on the drawbacks of these things, consciousness is not conceived. "

msgctxt "sn12.59:3.2"
msgid "Viññāṇanirodhā nāmarūpanirodho … pe … "
msgstr "When consciousness ceases, name and form cease. … "

msgctxt "sn12.59:3.3"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti. "
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn12.59:4.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, mahārukkho. "
msgstr "Suppose there was a great tree. "

msgctxt "sn12.59:4.2"
msgid "Atha puriso āgaccheyya kuddālapiṭakaṃ ādāya … pe … "
msgstr "Then a person comes along with a spade and basket. … "

msgctxt "sn12.59:4.3"
msgid "āyatiṃ anuppādadhammo. "
msgstr "In this way the great tree is cut off at the root, made like a palm stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.59:4.4"
msgid "Evameva kho, bhikkhave, saṃyojaniyesu dhammesu ādīnavānupassino viharato viññāṇassa avakkanti na hoti. "
msgstr "In the same way, there are things that are prone to being fettered. When you concentrate on the drawbacks of these things, consciousness is not conceived. "

msgctxt "sn12.59:4.5"
msgid "Viññāṇassa nirodhā nāmarūpanirodho … pe … "
msgstr "When consciousness ceases, name and form cease. … "

msgctxt "sn12.59:4.6"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hotī”ti. "
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.59:4.7"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

